Package biblioteka.core

Class Zurnalas

java.lang.Object
biblioteka.core.Leidinys
biblioteka.core.Zurnalas
All Implemented Interfaces:
Borrowable, Postponable, Serializable
public class Zurnalas extends Leidinys
Represents a physical magazine or journal in the library. This class extends Leidinys and adds magazine-specific details such as issue number, editorial office, publication month, ISSN, and theme.
